quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  8,34,"Nabo bali nende lilayi shina lia Nyasaye alabahelesia eshinyasio, nikali mbu bekalilanga Abandu omusikiti okwoluyali oko, Ne shini abaliindi bakwo tawe, toto abalindi bakwo nibalia abaria Nyasaye, ne obunji mubo shibamanyile shiosi shiosi tawe"
  8,35,Ne isaala yabu munzu yoluyali shiyali halali okhupa emilosi nende amakhofi. Kho pile eshinyasio shingala mwakhayanga
  8,36,"Toto balia abakhaya barusinjia omwandu kwabu okhwikalila injila ya Nyasaye, betsa okhukurusia mana kalababeela ameyitsulisio mana balashilwa. Ne balia abakhaya balikhung’asibwa mumulilo"
  8,37,"Kho Nyasaye anyoole okhwawukhasia ababii nende abalayi, nende okhura abamabii hekulu ewa abamabii bandi nende okhubabumba boosi halala nende okhubasukuna mumulilo. Abo nibo banyoola okhusikha"
  8,38,"Boolela balia bakhaya mbu; “Nibalekha, balaleshelwa akabura, ne nibakalushila, kamala okhubaburira amachelasio ka bandu bakhale.”"
  8,39,"Ne khupane ninabo okhuula mumale amatemo nende okhusandibwa. Ne idini ibe yosi shichila Nyasaye. Ne nibalekha, awo toto Nyasaye alolanga muno akabakholanga"
  8,40,Ne ni bakalukhana manye mbu Nyasaye niye Omwami wenyu ni Omulesi nende Omukhoonyi Omulayi